data.description: Welcome to this charming, updated 2-bedroom, 1-bathroom home nestled in the heart of a vibrant neighborhood, offering both comfort and convenience. Step inside to discover a thoughtfully designed open layout that seamlessly blends modern style with functionality. Remodeled in 2021, this spacious living area welcomes you with abundant natural light and a comfortable atmosphere, perfect for relaxation or entertaining guests. The stylish kitchen features granite countertops, stainless steel appliances, and ample, well thought out storage, perfect for culinary enthusiasts. The bathroom features contemporary fixtures and a refreshing ambiance, and the shower is powered by a tankless water heater. Outside, you'll find an expansive yard ideal for outdoor activities or enjoying a morning coffee. Situated near highway 36, 70, and 76 this location will give you easy access to downtown Denver, Boulder, and also point you on a direct path to the Rockies. With its prime location and modern amenities, this home offers the perfect opportunity for those seeking comfortable and stylish living in a great neighborhood. Don't miss out on making this your new home sweet home! Open House Saturday 2/10/24 2PM-4PM
